OL,6,FGerry Adams' defamation case against
OL,7,Fthe BBC has begun at the High Court in
OL,8,FDublin.
OL,10,FA jury was sworn in on Tuesday morning.
OL,12,FThe former Sinn Fein president alleges
OL,13,Fthat the broadcaster defamed him in a
OL,14,FSpotlight documentary programme and on
OL,15,Ftheir website in 2016.
OL,17,FThe documentary focused on the killing
OL,18,Fof Denis Donaldson, a former member of
OL,19,Fthe IRA who later admitted to being an
OL,20,Finformant to British security and
OL,21,Fintelligent forces.
